title: fly me to the moon (live 1965)
lyrics: Fly me to the moon Let me play , up there with those the stars Let me see what life is like On a Jupiter and Mars In other words, hold my hand In other words, darling kiss me Fill my heart with song And let me swing ,for ever more You are all I long for All I worship and adore In other words, please be true In other words, i love you Why don't you fill heart with song Let me sing , for ever more Because you are i worship All i long for and adore In other words , please be true In other words , in other words i......love....you
